::Havoc/Repressor::

Havoc nods. "Earth it is then. Repressor, get us out of here."

Repressor taps a few buttons, speeding up as the craft enters the transwarp 
portal, shaking like it was about to explode....
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The ship emerges in the atmosphere above earth, quickly plummeting down to 
the green planet. Demolition had been right, Havoc thought as he glanced at 
the scanners, the police hadn't followed.

"Brace for impact!" Havoc yells, seconds before the ship hits the ground. 
Havoc is thrown into a panel, everything going black. Near him, Repressor 
slams through a chair, flipping over a console and hitting the wall.
